data.description: Welcome to the exquisite Oak Creek neighborhood, where luxury living meets convenience. This is the only gated community with 24 hour security personnel in PG County. This stunning townhome boasts three bedrooms, four bathrooms, and an unbeatable location just a 3-minute walk from an 18-hole golf course. With 24-hour security, a golf course, club house, and a sparkling swimming pool, this prime community offers an outstanding buying opportunity. Don't miss out on this rare chance to own a piece of this exclusive neighborhood. Your discerning buyers will appreciate this deal, making it a valuable investment you won't want to pass up.
